      <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" id="input" placeholder="Copy and paste the matrix numbers in this box (no need of entering the matrix order) and click Calculate Determinant OR Enter the matrix manually (row-wise and separated by spaces) and then click Calculate Determinant."></textarea>
